reviews.review_text: BARNEY THE PURPLE DIONSAUR! Standard show. Rained like cats and dogs! Nice recording. Does anyone remember BARNEY THE PURPLE DINOSAUR playing bass on Iko?!!!!

- This was the Barney show? Phil Lesh talked about that in his autobiography. As I write this, Phil will be playing 80 miles away tomorrow at the Crystal Ballroom in Portland, and I'm missing it, which sucks. Anyway, this show is pretty good, but there are much better shows from this year.
